294
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:28,440
You didn't accompany Siyu to the training school that day

295
00:13:30,440 --> 00:13:31,520
to help her out.

296
00:13:33,360 --> 00:13:34,760
Think whatever you want.

297
00:13:36,280 --> 00:13:39,480
You went to investigate the clue the mystery man gave you.

298
00:13:40,400 --> 00:13:42,400
The mystery man's clue only appeared for a second,

299
00:13:42,400 --> 00:13:43,660
but you remembered it.

300
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:51,130
What exactly are you trying to say?

301
00:13:54,560 --> 00:13:55,320
This case

302
00:13:56,560 --> 00:13:58,820
should also be related to the Scavenger.

303
00:13:59,520 --> 00:14:00,780
The Scavenger is dead.

304
00:14:01,320 --> 00:14:02,200
You shot him.

305
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:06,480
I won't let you follow in your father's footsteps.
